Package: epmr
Title: Tools for Educational and Psychological Measurement
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Anthony", "Albano", email = "tony.d.albano@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/talbano/epmr
Description: Contains tools for creating and evaluating educational and
    psychological measures, as used in the book Introduction to Educational and
    Psychological Measurement: Using R. Methods support statistical analysis of
    item performance, reliability, validity, and dimensionality, within both
    classical and item response theory frameworks. Example data come from the 2009
    PISA study and the BDI-II.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: lme4, dplyr, tibble, ggplot2
Encoding: UTF-8
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
